fields.title: Fantasy Landscape with Magical Elements
fields.content: Create a mystical forest scene with glowing mushrooms, ethereal lighting, and fantasy art style. Include floating islands in the background, crystal formations, and magical particles in the air. Use vibrant colors like deep purples, blues, and greens with golden highlights.
fields.excerpt: Mystical forest scene with glowing mushrooms, ethereal lighting, fantasy art style

fields.title: Cyberpunk Cityscape at Night
fields.content: Generate a futuristic cyberpunk city at night with neon lights, flying cars, and rain-soaked streets. Include towering skyscrapers with holographic advertisements, blade runner aesthetic, and dramatic lighting with pink and blue color schemes.
fields.excerpt: Futuristic cyberpunk city with neon lights, flying cars, rain-soaked streets

fields.title: Minimalist Product Photography Setup
fields.content: Create a clean, minimalist product photography setup with soft lighting, neutral background, and elegant shadows. Perfect for showcasing products with professional commercial photography style, clean aesthetic, and subtle reflections.
fields.excerpt: Clean minimalist setup with soft lighting, neutral background, elegant shadows

fields.title: Abstract Digital Art with Geometric Patterns
fields.content: Design abstract digital artwork featuring geometric patterns, gradient colors, and modern design elements. Include flowing shapes, mathematical precision, and contemporary art style with bold color combinations and dynamic composition.
fields.excerpt: Abstract digital art with geometric patterns, gradients, modern design

fields.title: Vintage Travel Poster Design
fields.content: Create a vintage-style travel poster with retro typography, classic color palette, and nostalgic design elements. Include iconic landmarks, art deco styling, and promotional travel poster aesthetic from the 1930s-1950s era.
fields.excerpt: Vintage travel poster with retro typography, classic colors, art deco styling

fields.title: Character Design for Fantasy RPG
fields.content: Design a fantasy RPG character with detailed armor, magical weapons, and epic fantasy styling. Include character sheet elements, multiple poses, and concept art approach with rich details and fantasy game aesthetic.
fields.excerpt: Fantasy RPG character with detailed armor, magical weapons, epic styling
